{"tid":1398263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［人手置頂］零售從業員聯署過700大關","createTime":"2019-08-02T17:47:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T05:35:01.000Z","uid":195403,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"83ab46d0ca7fdb9413a6a1ce961b8819d51576e6","tid":1398263,"uid":195403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:47:10.000Z","msg":"零售界呼籲八月五日全民罷工之聲明<br />\n<br />\n我們是一群零售從業員，有見近期香港因《逃犯條例》引起嚴重社會撕裂，但特區政府於個多月來置若罔聞，我們每天面對市民，深感有需要在此時為香港站出來。<br />\n<br />\n我們特別關注警隊嚴重濫權的問題，尤其於七月十四日警隊不合理闖入沙田新城市廣場，直接造成混亂場面，打破商場的安寧，對市民及商戶皆造成極大影響。另外，警方於七月廿一日懷疑故意放任黑幫於元朗站無差別攻擊市民，並以惡劣態度對待市民及遊客，嚴重打擊香港形象，多個國家更因此對香港發出旅遊警告，對香港零售業造成沉重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n雖然近月的持續遊行對生意額造成不小打擊，但我們深明長痛不如短痛之理，現呼籲各位同事於八月五日一同響應罷工，以和平手段迫使政府正視問題根源，不要繼續使用軍政府的獨裁手法對付香港市民。<br />\n<br />\n現促請政府盡快回應以下訴求：<br />\n1. 成立獨立調查委員會；<br />\n2. 調查七月廿一日元朗事件涉嫌警黑合作；<br />\n3. 正式撤回《逃犯條例》；<br />\n4. 撒銷暴動定性；<br />\n5. 釋放所有被捕的抗爭者；<br />\n6. 立即實行雙普選。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我們希望大家牢記香港開埠已經一百七十八年。一直以來，香港經歷過無數風風雨雨，我們都依然能昂首向前，倚靠的正是我們團結一致的精神。我們衷心希望香港這次能跨過難關，攜手向前，願我們這一代香港人能重建香港往昔的榮光。<br />\n<br />\n並呼籲顧主要體恤員工，對罷工員工作出彈性處理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各界零售從業員聯署<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8月2日為止聯署已超過700人</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nTelegram:<br />\n <a href=\"http://t.me/retailhk85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fretailhk85&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=a767df47\" target=\"_blank\">t.me/retailhk85</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook: <br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E6%A5%AD%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-106602347350065/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259B%25B6%25E5%2594%25AE%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F-106602347350065%2F&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=b7978440\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E6%A5%AD%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F-106602347350065/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推啊！</span>"},{"pid":"4acf342e19fd29c75fe424cf1a55d1fd347b88b8","tid":1398263,"uid":195403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:48:54.000Z","msg":"做7-11 百佳 fila Ikea omega Zara Dior Chanel乜都有"},{"pid":"911afd11b96ddc49d31a81f19d63d0a32a293dbf","tid":1398263,"uid":195403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:51:11.000Z","msg":"上咗蘋果 不過fb冇 所以好似冇乜人知<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190802&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59889612\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190802%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59889612&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDS%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=ea36e7cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190802%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59889612&h=5f814e74\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190802&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59889612</a>"},{"pid":"7a8bc0beebbd62b53c249fc29ff38d1813084a81","tid":1398263,"uid":195403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:56:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8rwnzts.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8rwnzts.png&h=568feb35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa2209af489dd89f039f08307cc16726ba7ab2dd","tid":1398263,"uid":195403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:59:38.000Z","msg":"需要更多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2657097ee23e5de37dc9dd778bda50f8a6dc776b","tid":1398263,"uid":195403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=