:46:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d5bd7b5dc73dbdf719792e1c8c7d385e4a42ff7e","tid":1398263,"uid":195403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T01:37:08.000Z","msg":"今日跨界記者會無法出席"},{"pid":"9414b1885db94a97838a2a4f3e83fd81ac984286","tid":1398263,"uid":195403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:41:52.000Z","msg":"今天我們無法出席跨界記者會，我們感激零售業界踴躍聯署，沒有新聞報導下，兩日時間收到了700個聯署，當中包括食品、家品、時裝、鐘錶珠寶和藥房的零售從業員，聯署仍陸續增加。<br />\n<br />\n我們零售業者不是「見錢開眼」，讓香港撥亂反正比起佣金更為重要。<br />\n<br />\n在此，並呼籲顧主要體恤員工，保障員工安全，促顧主對罷工員工作出彈性上班處理。<br />\n感謝<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n<br />\n香港零售業罷工大聯盟<br />\n<br />\n2019.8.3"},{"pid":"a9b16517caef1dd73fcd752050d0196fa079a09e","tid":1398263,"uid":195403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:13:03.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d15042409c9e6b56bc0de47e1992b3c92c938814","tid":1398263,"uid":185991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:16:44.000Z","msg":"有人怪生意差<br />\n希望佢地快啲明白 再唔反抗<br />\n遲啲屎都無得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99602b6269b16bd74b73949d182d3c743dfe8a80","tid":1398263,"uid":195403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d15042409c9e6b56bc0de47e1992b3c92c938814","tid":1398263,"uid":185991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:16:44.000Z","msg":"有人怪生意差<br />\n希望佢地快啲明白 再唔反抗<br />\n遲啲屎都無得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T05:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd